      class  MoonEvent
      The class extends of Event class, gathers the calculations of Moon The calculations are: Rise and set Time, HorizonToHorizonCrossing type, Time meridianCrossing (noon), Time antimeridianCrossing (Midnigth), Position (rightAscention, declination, longitudeEcliptic and distance)
